title: Game of Thrones - Season 3[CENSORED]
description:
Gonna keep this short, these are the episodes from season 3 censored(as in no nudity, still cussing and violence). There may still be a little nudity, but nothing major.

I didn't make these files, I'm just re-uploading them, because they were removed and people were requesting them. I did however censor previous seasons, and plan to censor season 4.


Gonna try and cover everyone's concerns in a quick FAQ.

FAQ[PLEASE READ BEFORE COMMENTING]:

Why did you make this?
-I didn't and since it was removed, I'd prefer not to say.


Why did you upload it?
-I had it downloaded, it was removed, and people wanted it.

-Not all episodes had nudity, so just get the other episodes from any other torrent.

Are there subtitles?

What about season 4?
-When it comes out, it will be censored on a weekly basis, by me.

I think that this is a horrible thing to do, and you are a bad person for uploading this filth to the internet.
